<name>Obsidian Media Writer</name>
<summary>A tool to create a live USB drive with Obsidian OS</summary>
<description>
<p>A tool to create a bootable live USB drive with Obsidian OS - a security-hardened Linux distribution based on Debian 12. Obsidian Media Writer can download and write Obsidian OS to your flash drive with ease.</p>
<p>Obsidian OS features comprehensive security hardening including kernel hardening, DROP-all firewall, MAC spoofing, memory wiping, and application sandboxing.</p>
<p>Obsidian Media Writer can also write other bootable ISOs loaded from your local disk.</p>
</description>
